MOHD. AZEEM V. DLSTRLCT JUDGE & ORS [1985] INSC 95; AIR 1985 SC 1118; 1985 (3) SCR 844; 1985 (2) SCC 550; 1985 (1) SCALE 1097 (23 April 1985)

 MISRA RANGNATH MISRA RANGNATH DESAI, D.A.
 
CITATION: 1985 AIR 1118 1985 SCR (3) 844 1985 SCC (2) 550 1985 SCALE (1)1097 
ACT:
 Uttar Pradesh Urban Buildings (Regulation Letting, Rent and Eviction) Act 1972, section 12 (3) read with section 3 (a) and 3 (g)-Interpretation of the phrase "if the tenant or any member of his family" occurring therein-Deemed cessation of the tenancy and Deemed vacancy of the tenanted premises, when occurs, explained-Right to occupy the tenanted premises by the heirs under section 12, clarified.
 
